title: Graham McTavish talks Bourbon, Middle-earth, New Zealand, & More!
description:
Today, we welcome actor Graham McTavish (Dwalin, The Hobbit Trilogy) to talk about his new adventure - his own line of spirits!  We also chat about his time in Middle-earth, the wonder of New Zealand, his penchant for Fantasy, Star Wars, and more!

Order your own bottle of Warchief or Keeper at https://mctavishspirits.com/
Please drink responsibly!
